name: Tithonus CZ-03
description: This is a picture of the Tithonus CZ-03 was taken around 1 year after the time when the first space shuttle landed on the planet Aeolus. This planet was discovered by Nasa 15 Years ago in 2032. It is 19 Light Years away and is 1.7x bigger than Earth. It is the Smallest Gas giant Nasa has ever discovered. This planet revolves around a white Dwarf too, The closest and only white Dwarf in our galaxy. It has a unique moon, by unique we mean that its the first ever moon that's made of gas. Scientists say it was hit by a aesteroid which resulted in a lot of gas come out of the atmosphere of the Planet forming the moon. A man mission on this planet is expected to take place next year.
